text: Victoria Rodríguez Clavijo (24 September 1931 – 15 July 2020) was a Spanish actress. She appeared in many Spanish theatre shows. She appeared in Spanish productions of Don Juan Tenorio and Hamlet. Rodríguez died in Madrid on 15 July 2020 from pneumonia, aged 88. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from pneumonia Category:Spanish movie actors Category:Spanish television actors Category:Spanish stage actors Category:Actors from Madrid
